# af3io
Utilities for AlphaFold 3 input/output files:
- Copy data pipeline output from existing results: [datafill.ipynb](examples-colab/datafill/datafill.ipynb) ([open in Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/github/jurgjn/af3io/blob/main/examples-colab/datafill/datafill.ipynb))
- Differences between input JSON files: [input_diff.ipynb](examples-colab/input_diff/input_diff.ipynb) ([open in Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/github/jurgjn/af3io/blob/main/examples-colab/input_diff/input_diff.ipynb))
